  "title": "Strategic Planning Manager (Digital)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Strategic Planning Manager (Digital)</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Good in handling Market Research (R&D) on Digital Technologies, Strategic Planning, R&D, Report Management and Case Management.</li><li><strong>Good knowledge of Digital Technology, Emerging National Security and Digitalisation.</strong></li><li><strong>Experience in strengthening the capability of the nation security, financial tracking and good understand of Technology.</strong></li><li>Good in providing Presentation of business plans and strategies to Stakeholders, Clients and Business Users.</li><li>Possess Cloud Platform (GCC, Azure, AWS) and Artificial Intelligence.</li><li>Demonstrated strong experience in handling Digital Application.</li><li>Strong in Market Research and Technologies, Strategic Planning, R&D, Report and Road Map.</li><li>Identify use cases, problem statement, liaise stakeholders/ clients.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Strong knowledge of Strategic Planning, Mapping and providing direction on Digitalisation and Emerging Technologies.</li><li>Strong in <strong>Enterprise Technologies and Digitalisation.</strong></li><li><strong>Proven track record in providing Strategy Planning, Mapping on Emerging Technology and Digitalisation for National Security.</strong></li><li><strong>Possess Government (Defence) domain.</strong></li><li>Good knowledge of Architecture (hardware, software, and network)</li><li>Strong stakeholder management and can work well across all teams</li><li>Deep understanding of technology, trends, and business processes to enable clients in their digital roadmaps.</li><li>Min. 10 years of experience in handling Digital Solution and Application.</li><li>Foster strategic relationship with key customers and identify key new initiatives or programmes to support customers better and grow business.</li><li>Singaporean Only!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We respect your privacy and all communication will be treated with confidentiality.</p><p>If you have meet the job requirements that we are looking for or wish to find out more on this role, please contact us or apply in-confidence to us with your updated resume in MS Words format to : kelvin@starcareerconsulting.com</p><p><br /></p><p>*Only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p><p><br /></p><p>Lee Kelvin (Reg. No. R1872625)</p><p>STAR CAREER CONSULTING PTE. LTD</p><p>EA License: 20C0353</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p>",
